Interface V1ScannerDialog.V1SelectedListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MainActivity
    Enclosing class:
    V1ScannerDialog

    public static interface V1ScannerDialog.V1SelectedListener
    Interface used to allow the owner/creator of the dialog to run some code a device is selected.

    This will only be called when a device is selected.
